      "raw": "Style Notes",
      "text": "82 BPM. Dark gothic orchestral R&B with slow pounding drums, ominous violins, deep piano, cellos, choir pads, sub-bass, digital glitches, notification sounds, email pings, ad fragments, and static. Mostly emotional singing. One short rap-rock spoken verse. The song is about searching for peace and order inside modern data chaos. Ending stays ambiguous.",
