        "group": null,
        "spoken": null,
        "descriptor": "Low"
      },
      "raw": "Male Vocal - Low",
      "text": "Inbox open like a wound\nred numbers climbing in my room\nEverybody needs a piece\nbut nobody asks if I can breathe",
      "lines": 4,
