        "descriptor": "Both"
      },
      "raw": "Pre-Chorus - Both",
      "text": "Scroll by scroll\nI lose the shape of me\nPing by ping\nI forget what silence means",
      "lines": 4,
      "startT": 87.39,
      "endT": 88.4,
      "bars": 1
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "id": "ceasefire-in-the-static-data-storm-version::chorus::6",
      "kind": "chorus",
      "ordinal": null,
      "voice": {
        "gender": null,
        "group": null,
        "spoken": null,
        "descriptor": "Big Gothic R&B"
      },
      "raw": "Chorus - Big Gothic R&B",
      "text": "I’m looking for a ceasefire in the static\none quiet place inside the noise\nA little room behind the panic\nwhere I can hear my real voice\nI’m looking for a pattern in the madness\na holy line through broken code\nIf peace is somewhere in the chaos\nthen I’m still walking down that road",
      "lines": 8,
      "startT": 88.4,
      "endT": 89.12,
      "bars": 1
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "id": "ceasefire-in-the-static-data-storm-version::verse-2::7",
      "kind": "verse",
      "ordinal": 2,
      "voice": {
        "gender": "female",
        "group": null,
        "spoken": null,
        "descriptor": "Female"
      },
      "raw": "Verse 2 - Female",
      "text": "Ads in my dreams\nghosts in my feed\nEvery open window\nopens something else in me\nMessages stack like stones\non a chest that won’t let go\nI keep answering the world\nbut I don’t answer my own soul",
      "lines": 8,
      "startT": 89.12,
      "endT": 98.16,
      "bars": 3
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "id": "ceasefire-in-the-static-data-storm-version::other::8",
      "kind": "other",
      "ordinal": null,
      "voice": {
        "gender": "male",
        "group": null,
        "spoken": null,
        "descriptor": null
      },
      "raw": "Male Vocal",
      "text": "I tried to name the storm\nfolders for the pain\nTags for every memory\nrules for every flame\nBut every time I clear the screen\nanother wave comes back\nAnother voice, another need\nanother signal dressed in black",
      "lines": 8,
      "startT": 98.16,
      "endT": 110.64,
      "bars": 4
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "id": "ceasefire-in-the-static-data-storm-version::verse::9",
      "kind": "verse",
      "ordinal": null,
      "voice": {
        "gender": null,
        "group": null,
        "spoken": true,
        "descriptor": null
      },
      "raw": "Short Rap-Rock Spoken Verse",
      "text": "Too many tabs, too many chains\ntoo many faces with borrowed names\nToo many alerts in the bloodstream\ntoo many ghosts in the lockscreen\nI’m not lost, I’m overloaded\nheart still here, just overcoded\nTrying to breathe through the interface\ntrying to find one sacred space",
      "lines": 8,
      "startT": 110.64,
      "endT": 124.64,
      "bars": 5
    },
